{"id":"rcl-95y","title":"Rename repo to cross-framework-ui-design-system","description":"Rename the repo from 'react-component-library' to 'cross-framework-ui-design-system' — the 'react' name is misleading now that the project is a cross-framework design system (React 18 + Svelte 5) built on design tokens and contract-based component libraries.\n\nNew repo: https://github.com/NeuralEmpowerment/cross-framework-ui-design-system\n\nScope:\n- Rename the GitHub repo (Settings > rename) — GitHub auto-redirects the old URL.\n- Update git remote: git remote set-url origin https://github.com/NeuralEmpowerment/cross-framework-ui-design-system.git\n- Update references to the old name/path: README, CLAUDE.md/AGENTS.md, package.json (root name, repository.url), docs, any CI/badges.\n- Update local clone directory name (optional): react-component-library -> cross-framework-ui-design-system.\n- Note: npm package scope (@design-system/*) is unaffected; this is only the repo identity.\n\nConsidered alternatives: 'design-system' (matches @design-system scope but doesn't signal cross-framework); 'cross-framework-design-system' (no 'ui').","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"chore","created_at":"2026-06-16T20:17:02.591975Z","created_by":"neural","updated_at":"2026-06-16T20:17:02.591975Z","source_repo":"react-component-library","source_repo_path":"/Users/neural/Code/node/react-component-library","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
